    "| Weather  | Played | No | Total |\n",
    "|----------|------|----|-------|\n",
    "| Sunny    | 3    | 2  | 5     |\n",
    "| Overcast | 4    | 0  | 4     |\n",
    "| Rainy    | 2    | 3  | 5     |\n",
    "| Total    | 9    | 5  | 14    |   \n",
    "    \n",
    "Bu tabloya göre $ \\mathbb{P}(played | weather) $ şöyle:\n",
    "    \n",
    "| Weather  | Proba(Played\\|Weather) | Proba(No\\|Weather) |\n",
    "|----------|----------------------|--------------------|\n",
    "| Sunny    | 3/5 = 0.6                  | 2/5 = 0.4                |\n",
    "| Overcast | 4/4 = 1.0                  | 0/4 = 0.0                |\n",
    "| Rainy    | 2/5 = 0.4                  | 3/5 = 0.6                |\n",
    "    \n",
    "</details>"
   ]
